<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="12Apr1929"><font color="red">12 April 1929</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I am very busy revising the fragment and don&apos;t feel at all well &hellip; Have you a copy of Blast II and is it possible to have that Welsh-English dictionary? &hellip; I hope to finish my revision in a week or so. </div>
